id":"4c8a7fd24c0dc35fd7fa549e6a907d3404418b58","tid":523070,"uid":36901,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"1.暴力<br />\n2.過於緊張<br />\n3.過於放縱<br />\n<br />\n都係大忌，小朋友最重要係明辯是非，唔係聽教聽話"},{"pid":"d665ae26279d7b5588db9ec3477ed599a60110f6","tid":523070,"uid":128014,"like":9,"dislike":14,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:01:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 第N屆Lihkg童年鬥慘大賽正式開始</span><br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細個被阿媽打到癱咗，但我淚都無流過一滴。因為我知道哭是沒有用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大個咗就係深圳南山區有自己嘅上市公司，近排隻股票仲升到430蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c517695fd514c82f3eed327dec0c22e4fba2679","tid":523070,"uid":162864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"我係果種受軟唔受硬既人<br />\n<br />\n老豆老母勁鬧我都冇乜野 <br />\n<br />\n但佢地講親經我就會忍唔住想流馬尿<br />\n<br />\n其實以理服人一定好過用暴力 <br />\n<br />\n會有反效果。"},{"pid":"58742bb147361fbc08eb78560827a663a46ff388","tid":523070,"uid":99028,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fa07a0d191790c4c780d8a2bac547c4d523b8fb","tid":523070,"uid":26711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係華人先鐘意用打黎教仔, <br />\n<br />\n鬼佬係講道理, 同仔女傾, <br />\n<br />\n結果華人社會拍馬都追唔上鬼佬社會</blockquote>華人鬼佬分別係其一<br />\n有冇錢都係一個因素<br />\n諗下有錢佬點教仔就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD窮撚一黎冇家教 佢老豆老母點打仔佢就點打仔<br />\n二黎冇時間教<br />\n因為打鳩佢一定快過同佢講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢/冇心機教就咪撚生啦</blockquote>其實都睇社會狀況年代<br />\n打仔呢套六七十年代好似真係work</blockquote><br />\n係因為六七十年代唔文明 所以會work"},{"pid":"4657524df87954fbac52ee85c15afa8f49f3b276","tid":523070,"uid":139139,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"我老母叫我去學打拳<br />\n學完之後反而唔夠膽打人<br />\n淨係人哋會傷害我嘅時候先會還擊<br />\n<br />\n其實細路仔學打拳會自律好多<br />\n<br />\n到咗中一嘅時候<br />\n我老母唔想我食煙<br />\n所以佢就先拔頭籌<br />\n整咗一支紅盒萬寶路俾我試吓<br />\n最後我到而家都唔食煙<br />\n<br />\n阿媽細細個就教我飲酒<br />\n到咗依家三個鐘頭內飲兩支威士忌先會嘔<br />\n<br />\n其實你越唔想個仔做<br />\n佢就越想做<br />\n所以你先俾佢做<br />\n叫佢感受下"},{"pid":"e7ee7a19c56b9ab60fb48b975ab37a01ffe3884a","tid":523070,"uid":91931,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"有D仆街成日講到唔撚打點撚教<br />\n鬼佬咪又咁教<br />\n一係你同我講華人天生賤種<br />\n唔打唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地又點會承認"},{"pid":"4ee51bb56de7f39bdd16b8e69c191a51b04604ca","tid":523070,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:08:07.000Z","msg":"連登仔話晒都係年青廢老<br />\n點會唔撐"},{"pid":"185fbe38b0ead888d84326fd7a2f2084c3299fa4","tid":523070,"uid":18271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f915c4bbe78432c2bad6a890b9233a6a5cd376a4","tid":523070,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":37,"score":-34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔讚成體罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係哩代連手打都崖唔到，會唔會弱d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：細個老豆先過用水候通打我，我識用牛皮膠紙個圈做鎧甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁廢？我老母用刀斬架喎"},{"pid":"0237f6d13d01e0f91dcd325067aaaf988b768e8f","tid":523070,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a718eb0f4eafff05e5f879c47689fe38a111746c","tid":523070,"uid":17116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"宜家我屋企人應該好後悔細個打我  一爆計