6.000Z","msg":"真心, 唔打咁應該點教"},{"pid":"03d414d8a4af249bf46580731574f0fba7377c29","tid":523070,"uid":29161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"打就無問題<br />\n最緊要獎罰分明啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n90後有邊個唔係比老豆老母打大㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9417640b268b085fa27afe262b90b3021aa504","tid":523070,"uid":116014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eede22f19ce587ecd0a3b0aae043d6e44fce215","tid":523070,"uid":72009,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"有時子女唔聽話，父母好大責任，例如經常見父母餵食幼兒時俾ipad 手機佢地看，一扭計就俾手機卡通子女看，好多到小學已經沉迷手機，跟著父母又屌佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:21:17.000Z","msg":"完全認同, 我見好多都係咁。開頭又係你比個仔睇, 之後又要吊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ced30b58ae837829aa48e90b5fd8ad2a34a3ba","tid":523070,"uid":115644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"細個俾人用電蚊拍電，以前果啲電蚊拍係冇出邊果層鐵的，真係得通電果層果隻。<br />\n<br />\n我都唔支持體罰，暴力一定唔可以有效建立小朋友既價值觀的。有心教就睇多啲兒童心理學既書啦。<br />\n<br />\n台灣最近有單新聞係話個細路亂禁排籌果啲飛，佢老母教得佢幾好呀"},{"pid":"3598e39b864675f3acf9142b8ae0f73a7b53718f","tid":523070,"uid":99584,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0be5407e9a7f8e894d0b990f624d074d70c91fc6","tid":523070,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"少少事就打, 唔怪得而家d廢老講唔過人就打人"},{"pid":"86fc9e84221471d6acf81c2a3bc9e3c3fa702724","tid":523070,"uid":7805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"80af6d7fafe1fbd180852eecff33f76322751fd3","tid":523070,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"真心, 唔打咁應該點教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"個個人都應該問下自己呢個問題<br />\n無答案嘅就唔好生仔唔該曬"},{"pid":"a85b242f2274b7decd478d30135debb797473b7c","tid":523070,"uid":87230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"風和太陽的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ba3ae446944570e07075071a0a365ab21a6dae","tid":523070,"uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"80af6d7fafe1fbd180852eecff33f76322751fd3","tid":523070,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"真心, 唔打咁應該點教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"有天，我係麥記見有個小朋友玩手機唔食野，佢阿媽勸了幾次唔聽，之後話再過5秒唔收就大十倍聲叫佢收，等佢俾所有人望，小朋友立即自己收。 之後兩母子有講有笑。<br />\n<br />\n有時見Ｄ父母暴力搶機，同依位C9比真係失敗！"},{"pid":"be2b5e49030d7b3f8328ab61a00f20599b0164e8","tid":523070,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86fc9e84221471d6acf81c2a3bc9e3c3fa702724","tid":523070,"uid":7805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"80af6d7fafe1fbd180852eecff33f76322751fd3","tid":523070,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"真心, 唔打咁應該點教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"個個人都應該問下自己呢個問題<br />\n無答案嘅就唔好生仔唔該曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"講得好, 唔識教就唔好生, <br />\n<br />\n唔係生出黎後問唔打要點教"}]}